    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Peumus boldus are hepatitis, gallstones, digestive issues, jaundice, liver cirrhosis, and pancreatitis, due to its hepatoprotective properties, which help prevent liver cell damage. Additionally, Peumus boldus has been proven to effectively dissolve kidney stones, reduce the risk of cholecystitis, lower high blood pressure, alleviate diarrhea, and treat skin conditions such as eczema and acne. Furthermore, its anti-inflammatory properties have been shown to reduce the symptoms of arthritis, while also providing relief from constipation and gastroenteritis. Moreover, Peumus boldus has been found to lower high cholesterol levels, prevent cancer through its antioxidant properties, and even treat hepatic encephalopathy. By reducing inflammation and stress, Peumus boldus also helps alleviate anxiety.",
