    "preparations_description": "The main herbal preparations of Peumus boldus are made to utilize its medicinal properties effectively. Boldo tea is a popular preparation, made by infusing dried leaves in hot water to treat digestive issues and reduce inflammation. Boldo infusion is another preparation, similar to tea but often left to steep for a longer period to increase its potency. Boldo tincture is a concentrated liquid extract that can be administered sublingually or added to water, ideal for its bitter and anti-inflammatory properties. Boldo capsules and decoction are also used, the former providing a standardized dose of active compounds and the latter a more intense extract, both effective in treating various health conditions.",
